  rulesTitle: Bluffy Chess Rules
  rulesText: "Big pieces are masked \u2014 your opponent can't see your real pieces!\n\nArrange
    your back rank before the game starts.\nBig pieces can move in ANY direction
    (Queen + Knight combined).\n\nAfter a big piece moves, opponent can:\n  \u2022
    Accept \u2014 the move stands\n  \u2022 Call Bluff \u2014 if the move is illegal
    with the real type:\n      Caught! \u2192 the piece dies\n      Wrong call \u2192
    you sacrifice a piece & mover rearranges"
